622			// Build an executor that calls agent.ExecuteBead in-process, then
623			// submits the result to the project's land coordinator. The
624			// coordinator (a single goroutine per projectRoot) serializes all
625			// target-ref writes for this project — this is the server-side
626			// implementation of the human-PR landing model. See ddx-8746d8a6
627			// for the rationale. Prior to this rewrite, runWorker never called
628			// LandBeadResult at all, so commits produced by server-managed
